{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 70,
    "name": "سُورَةُ المَعَارِجِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Ma'aarij",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Ascending Stairways",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 44,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5376,
        "text": "或る者が，下るべき懲罰に就いて問う。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5377,
        "text": "不信心者は，それを防ぐことは出来ない。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5378,
        "text": "階段の主，アッラーから（の懲罰）である。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5379,
        "text": "天使たちや聖霊（大天使ジブリール）は，一日にして，かれの許に登る，その（一日の）長さは，5万年である。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5380,
        "text": "だからあなたは，立派に耐え忍べ。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5381,
        "text": "本当にかれらは，それ（日）を遠いと思う。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5382,
        "text": "しかしわれは，それを近いと見る。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5383,
        "text": "天が溶けた銅のようになる日，",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5384,
        "text": "山々は，梳いた羊毛のようになり，",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5385,
        "text": "誰も友（の安否）を問うことはない。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5386,
        "text": "かれらは互いに顔を合わせることが出来ない程恐れる。罪ある者はその日，自分の罪を贖うために自分の子供たちを差し出そうと願うであろう。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5387,
        "text": "かれの妻や兄弟，",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5388,
        "text": "かれを庇った近親，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5389,
        "text": "自分を救えるならば，地上の凡てのものを挙げて贖うことを請い願うであろう。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5390,
        "text": "断じて出来ない。本当にかの（地獄の）炎は，",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5391,
        "text": "頭の皮まで剣ぎ取る。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5392,
        "text": "（正義に）背を見せて，背き去った者を召喚するであろう。",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5393,
        "text": "また蓄積し，隠匿の金を持つ者をも。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5394,
        "text": "人間は本当に忙しなく創られている。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5395,
        "text": "災厄に会えば歎き悲しみ，",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5396,
        "text": "好運に会えば物惜しみになる。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5397,
        "text": "だが礼拝に精進する者は，そうではない。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5398,
        "text": "礼拝を厳守している者，",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5399,
        "text": "またかれらの富が，公正であると認められている者，",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5400,
        "text": "物乞いする者や耐乏する者のために（施す者），",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5401,
        "text": "また審判の日の真実を確認している者，",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5402,
        "text": "またかれらの主の懲罰を恐れる者も。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5403,
        "text": "本当に主の懲罰から，安全であると考えるべきではない。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5404,
        "text": "また隠れたところ（貞節）を守る者，",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5405,
        "text": "かれらの妻や右手の所有する者に限っている場合は別で，罪にはならない。",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5406,
        "text": "しかしこれ以外に求める者は法を越えた者である。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5407,
        "text": "付託されたことや約束に忠実な渚，",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5408,
        "text": "証言に公正な者，",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5409,
        "text": "また礼拝を厳守する者。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5410,
        "text": "これらの者は栄誉を得て楽園の中に（住む）。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5411,
        "text": "今不信心者たちが，あなたの方に急いでいるのは何事か。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5412,
        "text": "右からまた左から，群になって。",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5413,
        "text": "かれらは皆至福の楽園に入ることを望むのか。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5414,
        "text": "いや，断じて出来ないことである。本当にわれは，かれらが知るものから，かれらを創ったのである。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5415,
        "text": "いや，われは東と西の主によって誓う。われにとっては可能である。",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5416,
        "text": "かれらよりも優れた（外の）者をもって，かれらに替えてやろう。われは，失敗することはないのである。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5417,
        "text": "だからあなたは，かれらを（虚栄に）浸らせ，戯れに任せるがよい。かれらが約束されている，その日の会見まで。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5418,
        "text": "かれらが墓から慌ただしく出て来る日。それはまるで（現世で）かれらが偶像神へと急いだように。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5419,
        "text": "かれらは目を伏せ，屈辱を被るであろう。これがかれらに約束されていた，その日である。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
